      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "If I can get a bit more of it done in the next week or two, yep! Would love to tape this out for Run2.  it's an \"event pixel\" design, where each pixel fires asynchronously when its threshold is breached. They register changes in a scene rather than a clocked frame",
